{"tid":1279853,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【颱風追擊】1904號熱帶氣旋 木恩 MUN（05W）","createTime":"2019-07-02T19:00:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T19:00:39.000Z","uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2d028442b4f2c011fd949da569ece72ff6091cc2","tid":1279853,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T19:00:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://imgur.com/Pskei0w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FPskei0w.png&h=13bd482a&s={SIZE}\" /><strong><span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins>颱風追擊：熱帶氣旋 木恩</ins></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1904號熱帶氣旋 木恩 MUN（05W）  </span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">來源：米克羅尼西亞<br />\n意義：雅浦語，六月的意思</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n【註】 發出颱風追擊帖，表示有熱帶氣旋在南海或西北太平洋一帶形成。　<br />\n為使大家有一個良好舒適的瀏覽環境，請不要張貼未經證實的風暴消息、使用簡體中文貼文、提及力場或洗版，謝謝合作。　<br />\n請勿直接張貼會自動更新的氣象圖片，請把圖片上傳至儲存空間後再轉貼在帖文上。謝謝。　<br />\n <br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">請關注<span style=\"color: red;\">氣象巴打&bull;高登氣象台</span>最新動態<br />\n[img]//<a href=\"http://imgur.com/z4brcbr.png[/img]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2Fz4brcbr.png%5B%2Fimg%5D&d=DMh58HXBMwQbarqDBIsRc5Khd8YmQljH21R%2F5cbT5WU%3D&h=fb2dbaf3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">imgur.com/z4brcbr.png[/img]</a> [img]//<a href=\"http://imgur.com/2v9xh70.png[/img]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2F2v9xh70.png%5B%2Fimg%5D&d=DMh58HXBMwQbarqDBIsRc5Khd8YmQljH21R%2F5cbT5WU%3D&h=3eca56bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">imgur.com/2v9xh70.png[/img]</a> <br />\n[img]//<a href=\"http://imgur.com/gnzQsWS.png[/img]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FgnzQsWS.png%5B%2Fimg%5D&d=DMh58HXBMwQbarqDBIsRc5Khd8YmQljH21R%2F5cbT5WU%3D&h=ecec2ac3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">imgur.com/gnzQsWS.png[/img]</a> [img]//<a href=\"http://imgur.com/7sNQ3N2.png[/img]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2F7sNQ3N2.png%5B%2Fimg%5D&d=DMh58HXBMwQbarqDBIsRc5Khd8YmQljH21R%2F5cbT5WU%3D&h=8093c087\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">imgur.com/7sNQ3N2.png[/img]</a></span></em><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以下圖片會自動更新，直至熱帶氣旋消散。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏</span> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\"><ins>◤熱帶氣旋路徑圖</ins></span></span> <br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://www.hko.gov.hk/wxinfo/currwx/nwp_1906.png\" /> <img data-no-cache src=\"http://www.hko.gov.hk/wxinfo/currwx/tc_1906.png\" /> <br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://www.hko.gov.hk/wxinfo/currwx/zoom_1906.png\" /> <br />\n▲香港天文台(HKO) <br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://www.jma.go.jp/jp/typh/images/zooml/1904-00.png\" /> <img data-no-cache src=\"http://www.jma.go.jp/jp/typh/images/zoom5l/1904-00.png\" /> <br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://www.jma.go.jp/jp/typh/images/zoom24l/1904-00.png\" /> <br />\n▲ 日本氣象廳 (JMA) <br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"https://pzal.ndbc.noaa.gov/collab/jtwc/products/wp0519.gif\" /> <img data-no-cache src=\"http://www.tropicalstormrisk.com/tracker/dynamic/images/201905W.png\" /> <br />\n▲ 聯合颱風警報中心 (JTWC) <br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://typhoon2000.ph/multi/data/MUN.PNG\" /><br />\n▲各機構綜合預測</strong>"}]}